Name: How, with tools?
Subhead: epubcheck

A Java tool for validating EPUB files. 

* http://code.google.com/p/epubcheck/
* OCF container structure, OPF and OPS mark-up, and internal reference consistency are checked
* run on command-line
* can run as a Java server-side app or used as a Java library

Trust me: run epubcheck _before_ you start testing in various e-readers.

<pre><code>~/epubfiles$ java -jar /opt/epubcheck/epubcheck-1.2.jar hw.epub 
Epubcheck Version 1.2

No errors or warnings detected
</code></pre>